  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add your lovely stepsister on your desktop. Make sure she is not stuck anywhere!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game allows you to add your stepsister  to your desktop on top of all other applications. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3615360/extras/b931b336b7e4aa200c84966fa73236a5.poster.avif?t=1747050296\" width=634 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3615360/extras/b931b336b7e4aa200c84966fa73236a5.webm?t=1747050296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3615360/extras/b931b336b7e4aa200c84966fa73236a5.mp4?t=1747050296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can <strong>move</strong> her around, <strong>change her size</strong> and <strong>rotate</strong> as you like</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stepsister will <strong>change her clothes</strong> times to times, but do not try to spy on her</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She has <strong>physic body</strong>, but do not look on it too much, she is your sister after all</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She is very restless and will and <strong>can get stuck</strong> in various objects, for example <strong>in the washing machine</strong>, help her!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She likes to talk in <strong>different languages</strong> and can have custom voice lines from <strong>workshop</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect <strong>achievements</strong> just for spending time with her</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3615360/extras/cef529c1cdfb27d66c1658afc5f19352.poster.avif?t=1747050296\" width=634 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3615360/extras/cef529c1cdfb27d66c1658afc5f19352.webm?t=1747050296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3615360/extras/cef529c1cdfb27d66c1658afc5f19352.mp4?t=1747050296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add your lovely stepsister on your desktop. Make sure she is not stuck anywhere!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game allows you to add your stepsister  to your desktop on top of all other applications. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3615360/extras/b931b336b7e4aa200c84966fa73236a5.poster.avif?t=1747050296\" width=634 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3615360/extras/b931b336b7e4aa200c84966fa73236a5.webm?t=1747050296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3615360/extras/b931b336b7e4aa200c84966fa73236a5.mp4?t=1747050296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can <strong>move</strong> her around, <strong>change her size</strong> and <strong>rotate</strong> as you like</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stepsister will <strong>change her clothes</strong> times to times, but do not try to spy on her</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She has <strong>physic body</strong>, but do not look on it too much, she is your sister after all</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She is very restless and will and <strong>can get stuck</strong> in various objects, for example <strong>in the washing machine</strong>, help her!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She likes to talk in <strong>different languages</strong> and can have custom voice lines from <strong>workshop</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect <strong>achievements</strong> just for spending time with her</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3615360/extras/cef529c1cdfb27d66c1658afc5f19352.poster.avif?t=1747050296\" width=634 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3615360/extras/cef529c1cdfb27d66c1658afc5f19352.webm?t=1747050296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3615360/extras/cef529c1cdfb27d66c1658afc5f19352.mp4?t=1747050296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
